&lt;div data-page-id=&quot;R5pEdqmJmoX3WtxIJiNjDTCKpUb&quot; data-lark-html-role=&quot;root&quot; data-docx-has-block-data=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-IdxIdWSMyoqD4TxNEYpjwCiDpQe&quot;&gt;About the Role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RCDod239Zo8KBZxH3wZjB3TUp1f&quot;&gt;RadixArk is looking for a Backend/Platform Engineer to build the API layer, control plane, and platform services that power SGLang and Miles in production. You&#39;ll design and implement the REST/gRPC APIs, authentication systems, multi-tenancy isolation, and monitoring infrastructure that thousands of developers and companies rely on. This role bridges high-performance inference/training systems with production-grade platform engineering.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-PNQ0dhVtqouI29xSCxPjofzMpje&quot;&gt;Requirements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;list-bullet1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Eiihd6nU7oUX3UxOg3cjeMESpld&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;4+ years experience building production backend systems, APIs, or platform infrastructure&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XYQQdWbb6oOmz9xzJtMjLLB1pJe&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Bachelor&#39;s or Master&#39;s degree in Computer Science, Engineering, or equivalent industry experience&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EmRSdMYDWoQWP1xbYdMj8wFhppb&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Strong proficiency in Python, Go, or Rust with production-quality code standards&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MZKXdfn9No00PcxiXMOjbbYpp3c&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Experience designing and building REST/gRPC APIs at scale&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-SGvadeTUTodQwTxmbMajSKQRpWb&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Solid understanding of distributed systems, databases, caching, and message queues&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-M2uAd86XDogv4LxbfR9js1iWp8e&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Experience with authentication, authorization, rate limiting, and multi-tenancy&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LSJ7d2xreoQn7yxTM1ajdvqqpYL&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Familiarity with cloud platforms (AWS, GCP, Azure) and Kubernetes&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GXImd4spnooU6Yxs4l5jRG8Upsb&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Experience with monitoring and observability tools (Prometheus, Grafana, DataDog)&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RpkVdjqEJoGFMLxZGoBjRvblped&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Understanding of ML serving infrastructure or high-throughput systems is a plus&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-QRJ6dESr4o0h2WxRCBtjdgQ4pqb&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;list-bullet1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VZ6tdmktcoSXVsx9b58jariqpFz&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Design and build production APIs for SGLang and Miles: REST/gRPC endpoints, client SDKs, API versioning&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AiqodVosOoOCrKxZh4YjXTtApHh&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Implement authentication, authorization, and rate limiting systems for multi-tenant deployments&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IyR7drVF9oorY7xdW6tjC1DJpag&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Build control plane infrastructure: job scheduling, resource allocation, model deployment management&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;l

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a Head of Business Development to build the BD function at RadixArk from the ground up. The BD team is the institutional memory of this company — maintaining active relationships across every customer we&#39;ve touched, detecting signals early, and ensuring nothing falls through the cracks. You&#39;ll design the system, build the team, and run it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role is equal parts relationship and rigor. You&#39;ll hold the relationship thread across a broad customer surface while tracking coverage rates, handoff volume, signal trends, and engagement quality — and translating that into clear intelligence for the broader commercial organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We move fast, operate with a sense of urgency, and expect the same from everyone on the team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Own&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team Building&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hire and develop a BD team; establish the culture, methodology, and cadence for maintaining customer relationships at scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define the norms for how the BD team operates — how we track, how we communicate, how we escalate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the BD team&#39;s contribution to our single source of truth: the shared tracking sheet used by both BD and Adoption&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Relationship Coverage&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain broad, active relationships across our full customer surface: early adopters, shallow contacts, and gated prospects we haven&#39;t yet engaged deeply&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and run regular check-in rhythms (watching channels) that give us continuous pulse on the market without requiring deep-dive bandwidth from the full team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide genuine relational continuity for customers when the Adoption team doesn&#39;t have capacity — not just placeholder outreach, but real emotional presence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Downstream Handoff&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify customers who are ready for deeper engagement and hand them off cleanly to the Adoption team — with full context, no gaps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure raw data on gated customers remains accessible and well-documented so the Adoption team can run market research without starting from zero&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategy &amp;amp; Intelligence&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the alert system for the company: surface important signals — bad news, emerging trends, inflection points — before they become surprises&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Synthesize BD observations into regular summaries and analyses that inform commercial strategy and resource allocation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the bidirectional feedback loop between the BD team and the Adoption team — make sure learning flows both ways&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide guidance on where the company should invest engagement resources and where to pull back&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Partnerships&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead partnership development with industry leaders, regional leaders, and category leaders or rising stars in the AI infrastructure ecosystem&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the full partnership lifecycle from prospecting to structuring to activation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Available for a in-office schedule with 5 days per week onsite at our Palo Alto office&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years of BD, sales, or partnerships experience, with meaningful time at a high-growth technology company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record building teams and systems from scratch — you know what it means to create culture and methodology, not just inherit

&lt;h2&gt;About the Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a Chief of Staff / Strategic Executive Assistant to partner directly with our founders and help scale the company through its next stage of growth. This is not a traditional Executive Assistant role. You&#39;ll be a trusted operator responsible for helping leadership stay focused on the highest-impact priorities while driving execution across the business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll own a mix of executive operations, strategic projects, cross-functional coordination, recruiting support, and company operations. One moment you may be preparing materials for an investor meeting; the next, coordinating an important hiring process, improving an internal workflow, or driving a cross-functional initiative to completion.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll report directly to the Head of Finance &amp;amp; Operations and work closely with the founders and leadership team. This is a unique opportunity to build the operational backbone of a fast-growing AI infrastructure company.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We move quickly, operate with urgency, and expect the same from everyone on the team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What You&#39;ll Own&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Executive Partnership&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Manage complex calendars, meetings, travel, and shifting priorities for company leadership&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Prepare agendas, briefing materials, meeting notes, and follow-up action items to ensure decisions turn into execution&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anticipate bottlenecks, proactively solve scheduling conflicts, and optimize executive time&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Handle confidential information with professionalism and sound judgment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Strategic Operations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Drive cross-functional projects that require coordination across engineering, research, recruiting, finance, and operations&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Track company priorities, key initiatives, and executive action items to ensure timely execution&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Support board meetings, investor updates, leadership offsites, and strategic planning efforts&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Research, synthesize information, and prepare presentations, reports, and internal documentation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Recruiting &amp;amp; People Operations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Partner with hiring managers to coordinate executive hiring and other key recruiting efforts&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Help deliver an exceptional candidate experience from scheduling through onboarding&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Support employee onboarding, internal communications, and company-wide operational initiatives&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Assist with planning team events, offsites, and culture-building activities&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Company Operations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Identify opportunities to improve internal processes and increase organizational efficiency&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Help build scalable operational systems as the company grows&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Coordinate with external vendors, partners, and service providers when needed&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Take ownership of high-priority special projects that support company growth&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Who You Are&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Available for a hybrid schedule with 3 days per week onsite at our Palo Alto office&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3–7 years of experience as a Chief of Staff, Executive Assistant, Strategic Operations, Program Manager, Management Consultant, or similar role&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree required&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Exceptional organizational and project management skills with the ability to manage multiple priorities simultaneously&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Highly proactive—you identify problems before they become blockers and consistently follow through&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Comfortable operating independently in an ambiguous, fast-changing startup environment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strong business judgment and the ability to handle confidential information with disc

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a Corporate Counsel to be our first in-house lawyer — and to build the legal foundation the company needs as we move from seed-stage into serious commercial and operational scale. This is not a narrow role. You’ll own everything from day-to-day contracts and commercial agreements to fundraising support, employment matters, IP, and compliance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll have access to outside counsel for specialized work, but we expect you to handle the majority of legal work internally, manage outside counsel efficiently, and bring genuine judgment — not just process — to everything you touch.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll report directly to the Head of Finance &amp;amp; Operations and work in close partnership with the founders. This is a rare opportunity to define what great looks like for Legal at RadixArk — and to build it yourself.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We move fast, operate with a sense of urgency, and expect the same from everyone on the team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Own&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Commercial Contracts&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Negotiate, structure, and close commercial agreements — MSAs, SaaS agreements, vendor contracts, and partnership deals — representing the company’s interests while keeping deals moving&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and manage NDA workflow end-to-end: reviewing inbound requests, redlining where appropriate, coordinating signatures, and maintaining a clean filing system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support, structure, and negotiate customer-facing revenue agreements as commercial activity scales; manage the related legal workstreams from first draft through execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Escalate novel structures or terms that create downstream risk; flag issues that matter while letting routine matters close without unnecessary friction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own our contracts repository and lifecycle management — tracking renewals, key dates, and obligations, and building lightweight processes to keep everything organized&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Corporate &amp;amp; Fundraising&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support strategic transactions, partnerships, financing, and any M&amp;amp;A or acqui-hire activity; understand how deal structures interact with operational and business objectives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support cap table integrity — stock option grants, 409A processes, and board and stockholder consents — in close partnership with finance and outside counsel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage corporate governance — maintaining records, coordinating board and committee matters, and ensuring the company is properly structured as it scales&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IP &amp;amp; Compliance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee IP protection — trademark filings, patent processes with outside counsel, and ensuring IP assignment and ownership is airtight across employees and contractors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor applicable regulatory and compliance requirements; provide proactive legal risk management rather than reactive triage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Outside Counsel Management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with specialized outside counsel across practice areas, ensuring their work product aligns with the company’s commercial objectives and moves at the pace the business requires&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Make smart build-vs.-refer decisions: handle what you can internally, escalate what genuinely requires specialization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Available for a hybrid schedule with 3 days per week onsite at our Palo Alto office&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4–7 years of legal experience, with a combination of law firm training and in-house experience at a technolo

&lt;div data-page-id=&quot;UU1fdpOOzoO34gxmPH2j7HOGpdf&quot; data-lark-html-role=&quot;root&quot; data-docx-has-block-data=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;heading-2 ace-line old-record-id-AQfIdzWqooQawBxo3uRj6hbIpfI&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WUMSdduJmofSS2xgPWljBWC7p4g&quot;&gt;RadixArk builds the open-source AI infrastructure behind SGLang and Miles, used by developers and enterprises around the world. We&#39;re looking for a designer to give our brand a distinct visual voice, led by illustration, and who treats modern AI tools as part of their craft rather than a novelty. Taste and ideas matter to us more than years on a resume, which is why we read portfolios first and care most about the work itself. You&#39;ll shape how RadixArk shows up everywhere from our site and decks to the conferences and community events we run. We care about craft and about building things that scale, so the best work here won&#39;t just set the quality bar, it&#39;ll become systems the whole team can build on. As our platform grows, there&#39;s a real path into product, so we want someone with the curiosity and range to grow into a product designer or design engineer over time.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;heading-2 ace-line old-record-id-PLqvd0pdMotc0GxarEBj0epgp6b&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;list-bullet1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-B2lPdo4Pvoi1BrxIvPZjSGMXpLc&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Create original illustrations that define and extend the RadixArk and SGLang visual identity&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LWxHd1rfaoFGvwxTmbhjxoVGpXT&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Build and steward a consistent brand system across every touchpoint&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-X4Tkdcqv0oJ64exZJmkjtBj0plh&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Use AI image tools (GPT Image 2, Nano Banana, and whatever comes next) to go from idea to polished asset quickly&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RITJdBPzhoGrhBxnz7ijmtvGpth&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Use Claude Code as a design tool, for example to prototype landing pages and interactive web experiences in code, generate SVG illustrations and icon sets, and build or maintain design-system components and tokens&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Sa4Rdr0EWoPJMXxWsa5jBhltpPe&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional partners across product, GTM, BD, engineering, and community to turn their goals into clear, compelling visuals and materials, both internal and external-facing, including conference and event collateral like slides, signage, booths, swag, and more&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZHKjdJKXaoWEa0xPaAJjXSMIpnm&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Produce a steady stream of visual content for blogs and social&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JvoVda8Iho93kNxEixKj9sCZpff&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Partner with the team on product and platform polish, with room to grow into a product design role&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;heading-2 ace-line old-record-id-IzTfd3wNgoQCDyxQqW4jaYWup42&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
