&lt;li&gt;Comfort engaging with engineering teams and asking good questions in technical conversations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ambition to grow into a hybrid seller-engineer role over time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Existing relationships across AI, cloud, or enterprise ecosystems are a plus&lt;/li&gt;
